## How to Run

```bash
# 1. Generate personas
python main.py generate-personas --count 20 --preview

# 2. Run simulation (Ollama — requires `ollama pull llama3.2`)
python main.py simulate --num-conversations 5

# 2b. Run simulation (Gemini — no Ollama needed)
python main.py simulate --num-conversations 5 --provider gemini

# 3. Validate output
python main.py validate data/conversations/conversations_*.jsonl
```

